ive limited portions (the EU introduced 14 such bans during the 28 months of the war).\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5795, \"end\": 5797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.9741366260705394e-15, \"text\": \"EU\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sanctions\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5681}, {\"ngram\": \"devastating effect\", \"from\": 5717, \"to\": 5735}, {\"ngram\": \"successive limited portions\", \"from\": 5762, \"to\": 5789}, {\"ngram\": \"14 such bans\", \"from\": 5809, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"the 28 months\", \"from\": 5829, \"to\": 5842}, {\"ngram\": \"the war\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 5853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aid to Ukraine is also being provided gradually, in ineffective installments.\", \"from\": 5857, \"to\": 5934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5864, \"end\": 5871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.164589244384865e-14, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ineffective installments\", \"from\": 5909, \"to\": 5933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, there was no consent to deliver state-of-the-art tanks or F-16 fighters, but now they are being sent, as well as long-range missiles capable of attacking targets on Russian territory.\", \"from\": 5935, \"to\": 6130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6112, \"end\": 6119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999986908787306, \"rank\": 1.271667102304464e-06, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no consent\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\":